{"problem":{"stackLimit":128,"modifiedUser":"root","auth":1,"isRemote":false,"description":"<p>若一个数（首位不为零）从左向右读与从右向左读都是一样，我们就将其称之为回文数。例如：给定一个 10进制数 56，将 56加 65（即把56从右向左读），得到 121是一个回文数。又如，对于10进制数87，<p><p>STEP1： 87＋78= 165 STEP2： 165＋561= 726<p><p>STEP3： 726＋627＝1353 STEP4：1353+3531=4884<p><p>在这里的一步是指进行了一次N进制的加法，上例最少用了4步得到回文数4884。<p><p>写一个程序，给定一个N（2＜N＜＝10或N=16）进制数 M．求最少经过几步可以得到回文数。如果在30步以内（包含30步）不可能得到回文数，则输出“Impossible” 。<p>","removeEndBlank":true,"uploadCase":true,"source":"","remote":false,"title":"回文数 ","type":0,"difficulty":1,"output":"<p>最少几步。如果在30步以内（包含30步）不可能得到回文数，则输出“Impossible”。<p>","timeLimit":1000,"input":"<p>给定一个N（2＜N＜＝10或N=16）进制数M。<p>","examples":"<input>9 87\n</input><output>6\n</output>","ioScore":10000,"codeShare":false,"hint":"","isRemoveEndBlank":true,"openCaseResult":true,"memoryLimit":256,"problemId":"T1309","isUploadCase":true},"languages":["C","C With O2","C++","C++ With O2","Java","Python3","Python2","Golang","C#"],"codeTemplates":[],"isSpj":false,"samples":[{"output":"1.out","input":"1.in","score":100},{"output":"2.out","input":"2.in","score":100},{"output":"3.out","input":"3.in","score":100},{"output":"4.out","input":"4.in","score":100},{"output":"5.out","input":"5.in","score":100},{"output":"6.out","input":"6.in","score":100},{"output":"7.out","input":"7.in","score":100},{"output":"8.out","input":"8.in","score":100},{"output":"9.out","input":"9.in","score":100},{"output":"10.out","input":"10.in","score":100}],"tags":["一本通在线评测"]}